## Key Insights

### Git vs Syncthing
- **Syncthing:** Syncs files, causes conflicts
- **Git:** Version control, preserves all changes
- **Together:** Files sync via Syncthing, versions tracked via Git

### AI Access
- Can see complete project history via `git log`
- Can diff between any versions
- Can checkout any commit
- Cannot see SSH private keys (security win)

### Security
- SSH keys per computer = compartmentalized security
- One compromised computer = only that key revoked
- AI never sees credentials when pushing

